'''葡萄籽精华素'''是[[葡萄|葡萄]]籽中[[工業|工業]]粹取出來的物質。粹取物中含有[[原花青素|原花青素]]<ref name="nih">{{cite web|url=https://nccih.nih.gov/health/grapeseed/ataglance.htm|title=Grape Seed Extract, Herbs at a Glance|publisher=US National Center for Complementary and Integrative Health, National Institutes of Health|date=September 2016|accessdate=2020-02-09|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401125950/https://nccih.nih.gov/health/grapeseed/ataglance.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。葡萄籽粹取物的品質是由其中[[原花青素|原花青素]]的組成成份所決定<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Rue |first1=Emily A. |last2=Rush |first2=Michael D. |last3=van Breemen |first3=Richard B. |title=Procyanidins: a comprehensive review encompassing structure elucidation via mass spectrometry |journal=Phytochemistry Reviews |date=9 May 2017 |volume=17 |issue=1 |pages=1–16 |doi=10.1007/s11101-017-9507-3|pmid=29651231 |pmc=5891158 }}</ref>。一般的葡萄籽粹取物中會含有95%的[[原花青素|原花青素]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Wanwimolruk |first1=S |last2=Phopin |first2=K |last3=Prachayasittikul |first3=V |title=Cytochrome P450 enzyme mediated herbal drug interactions (Part 2). |journal=EXCLI Journal |date=2014 |volume=13 |pages=869–96 |pmid=26417310|pmc=4464477}}</ref>。

